Quickstrike:





Quickstrike put the jaw of his cobra hand over Stingtra's shoulder. "Ah 
think we're all goin' out if he's Hell Beast's bot." He was just as eager as 
her, but he learned they were nothing to mess with. He thought there could 
be more around, setting an ambush. "Jus' wait." He didn't like doing that, 
but sub-commanders did things like this. He had to break habits to prevent 
from being another low rank.
